<p>藍色漸變的美人魚尾圖案，看上去很適合夏天的氛圍。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-534059 post-image" src="https://cfcdn.she.com/media/she.com/2022/08/381910-381910-WOJDWD.jpg" alt="Burberry簡約白色Tee穿出無添加少女味" width="810" height="386" /></p>
<p><a class="external-btn-a-left" href="https://go.skimresources.com?id=155763X1622032&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.farfetch.com%2Fhk%2Fshopping%2Fwomen%2Fburberry-mermaid-tail-print-cotton-t-shirt-item-16470924.aspx%3Fstoreid%3D9352&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.she.com%2F3BmVfGJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shop Now</a></p>
